      "content": "thanks, that helps. one thing i'm still struggling with for my paper is the \"social order\" part. some of the sources i'm looking at make it sound like the people advocating for this weren't just being hateful, but actually thought they were preventing riots or chaos by keeping communities separate. can you expand on that specific argument? like, what was the \"logic\" regarding how segregation supposedly maintained peace and stability? i just want to make sure i can explain their reasoning clearly before i tear it down.",
